  "excerpt": "New renderings for the forthcoming Las Vegas A’s MLB stadium were released earlier by BIG and HNTB ahead of the planned start of construction work later this year. The approximately $1.5 billion project was first announced in March of 2024 as a retractable roof design with 33,000 seats and the...",
