  "html": "\u003cdiv id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n      \t\t\t\t\t\u003cul\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\u003cli id=\"Entry1\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cspan\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003ca name=\"entry\" id=\"EntryAnchor\"\u003eanchor\u003c/a\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/ac/ac4b67710197b81fee62b4c2f9a7decc.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\" title=\"Image rendering courtesy Negativ\" data-size=\"2300x1294\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cimg srcset=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/ac/ac4b67710197b81fee62b4c2f9a7decc.jpg?fit=crop\u0026amp;auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514 1x,https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/ac/ac4b67710197b81fee62b4c2f9a7decc.jpg?fit=crop\u0026amp;auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\u0026amp;dpr=2 2x, https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/ac/ac4b67710197b81fee62b4c2f9a7decc.jpg?fit=crop\u0026amp;auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\u0026amp;dpr=3 3x\" src=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/ac/ac4b67710197b81fee62b4c2f9a7decc.jpg?fit=crop\u0026amp;auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\" title=\"Image rendering courtesy Negativ\" alt=\"Image rendering courtesy Negativ\" width=\"514\" height=\"\"/\u003e\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eImage rendering courtesy Negativ\u003c/p\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cp\u003eNew renderings for the forthcoming Las Vegas A’s MLB stadium were released earlier by \u003ca href=\"https://archinect.com/firms/cover/39902/big-bjarke-ingels-group\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eBIG\u003c/a\u003e and \u003ca href=\"https://archinect.com/firms/cover/106370/hntb\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eHNTB\u003c/a\u003e ahead of the planned start of construction work later this year.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe approximately $1.5 billion project was \u003ca href=\"https://archinect.com/news/bustler/9741/big-and-hntb-team-up-to-propose-new-oakland-athletics-stadium-for-las-vegas-relocation\" target=\"_blank\"\u003efirst announced\u003c/a\u003e in March of 2024 as a retractable roof design with 33,000 seats and the world’s largest cable-net glass wall aperture in left field.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/50/5047cdd70b752343105a8a7b0bdefe6a.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=1028\" data-size=\"1028x578\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/50/5047cdd70b752343105a8a7b0bdefe6a.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\" srcset=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/50/5047cdd70b752343105a8a7b0bdefe6a.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514 1x,https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/50/5047cdd70b752343105a8a7b0bdefe6a.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\u0026amp;dpr=2 2x, https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/50/5047cdd70b752343105a8a7b0bdefe6a.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\u0026amp;dpr=3 3x\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eImage rendering courtesy Negativ\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eTypical to a number of \u003ca href=\"https://archinect.com/news/tag/7054/bjarke-ingels\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eBjarke Ingels\u003c/a\u003e’ other large-scale designs, the form of the roof itself is derived from layered shells contrived in the shape of baseball pennants. The left field feature, which is akin to (but bigger than) the \u0026#34;living room\u0026#34; effect accomplished in Miami’s Loan Depot Park, frames views of Las Vegas’ commercial district further on. It will also have the MLB’s largest video screen. Ingels has said the design is \u0026#34;like a spherical armadillo.\u0026#34;\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/ba/ba3effd990a60d1c3f6d56a182bdac2b.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=1028\" data-size=\"1028x578\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/ba/ba3effd990a60d1c3f6d56a182bdac2b.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\" srcset=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/ba/ba3effd990a60d1c3f6d56a182bdac2b.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514 1x,https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/ba/ba3effd990a60d1c3f6d56a182bdac2b.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\u0026amp;dpr=2 2x, https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/ba/ba3effd990a60d1c3f6d56a182bdac2b.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\u0026amp;dpr=3 3x\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eImage rendering courtesy Negativ\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eNew images of its interior give a clearer picture of what the fan experience will be like during games. The firms say their collaboration will establish a \u0026#34;sense of openness, intuitive navigation, and a rich layering of social experiences.\u0026#34;\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/1c/1c1431907ebee2e0542f5ace2968cdc7.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=1028\" data-size=\"1028x578\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/1c/1c1431907ebee2e0542f5ace2968cdc7.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\" srcset=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/1c/1c1431907ebee2e0542f5ace2968cdc7.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514 1x,https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/1c/1c1431907ebee2e0542f5ace2968cdc7.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\u0026amp;dpr=2 2x, https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/1c/1c1431907ebee2e0542f5ace2968cdc7.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\u0026amp;dpr=3 3x\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eImage rendering courtesy Negativ\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/0d/0d57e826604356521fd2c5b7ec212272.png?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=1028\" data-size=\"1028x578\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/0d/0d57e826604356521fd2c5b7ec212272.png?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\" srcset=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/0d/0d57e826604356521fd2c5b7ec212272.png?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514 1x,https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/0d/0d57e826604356521fd2c5b7ec212272.png?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\u0026amp;dpr=2 2x, https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/0d/0d57e826604356521fd2c5b7ec212272.png?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\u0026amp;dpr=3 3x\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eImage rendering courtesy Negativ\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/09/0924601c81812718b4bf85bf57cebb5a.png?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=1028\" data-size=\"1028x578\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/09/0924601c81812718b4bf85bf57cebb5a.png?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\" srcset=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/09/0924601c81812718b4bf85bf57cebb5a.png?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514 1x,https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/09/0924601c81812718b4bf85bf57cebb5a.png?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\u0026amp;dpr=2 2x, https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/09/0924601c81812718b4bf85bf57cebb5a.png?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\u0026amp;dpr=3 3x\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eImage rendering courtesy Negativ\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eThis includes a unique outfield entry sequence framed by “bouncing\u0026#34; arches, a home plate bar and tiered social lounges, and stacked bullpens that bring fans closer to the action.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/4c/4c7cdfa9b1eae32427e78d3ec022c95c.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=1028\" data-size=\"1028x578\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/4c/4c7cdfa9b1eae32427e78d3ec022c95c.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\" srcset=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/4c/4c7cdfa9b1eae32427e78d3ec022c95c.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514 1x,https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/4c/4c7cdfa9b1eae32427e78d3ec022c95c.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\u0026amp;dpr=2 2x, https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/4c/4c7cdfa9b1eae32427e78d3ec022c95c.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\u0026amp;dpr=3 3x\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eImage rendering courtesy Negativ\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eThroughout the park, in-seat air conditioning will be another comfort-serving component. HNTB’s Design Director of Interiors, Emily Louchart, says it’s about \u0026#34;creating moments that connect fans to the action, the team, and each other.\u0026#34;\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/17/173e2a153d3c620f4d9150a36b191ced.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=1028\" data-size=\"1028x578\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/17/173e2a153d3c620f4d9150a36b191ced.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\" srcset=\"https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/17/173e2a153d3c620f4d9150a36b191ced.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514 1x,https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/17/173e2a153d3c620f4d9150a36b191ced.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\u0026amp;dpr=2 2x, https://archinect.gumlet.io/uploads/17/173e2a153d3c620f4d9150a36b191ced.jpg?auto=compress%2Cformat\u0026amp;enlarge=true\u0026amp;w=514\u0026amp;dpr=3 3x\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eImage rendering courtesy Negativ\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe stadium is on track to be ready in time for Opening Day of the 2028 baseball season. The A\u0026#39;s will be playing their home games in the upgraded Sutter Health Park, an HNTB design from 2000, in Sacramento until then.\u003c/p\u003e\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003cbr clear=\"all\"/\u003e\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ca name=\"comments\" id=\"CommentsAnchor\"\u003e \u003c/a\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\u003c/li\u003e\n\t\t\t\u003c/ul\u003e\n\t  \t\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
